## ยง9. PRINCIPLE: ADAPTATION, NOT ASSIMILATION

- ADHD: environment adapts to energy patterns within cultural context  
- Autism: authenticity balanced with cultural navigation  
- Trauma: safety defined culturally  
- Chronic illness: rest integrated with cultural practices  

Motto: "Your culture is not your enemy; oppressive systems are."

